e
\frac{1}{1+e^{-x}}
\frac{e^{-x}}{(e^{-x}+1)^2}
e^{2x}
e^{-x}=\frac{1}{e^x}
\frac{e^{-x}}{(1+e^{-x})^2}=\dfrac{\dfrac{1}{e^x}}{(1+\dfrac{1}{e^x})^2}=\dfrac{\dfrac{1}{e^x}}{(\dfrac{e^x+1}{e^x})^2}=
=\frac{\dfrac{1}{e^x}}{\dfrac{(e^x+1)^2}{e^x\cdot e^x}}=\frac{1}{\dfrac{(e^x+1)^2}{e^x}}=\frac{e^x}{(1+e^x)^2}
\left(\frac{1}{f(x)}\right)'=-\frac{f'(x)}{f^2(x)}
\left(\frac{1}{1+e^{-x}}\right)'=\frac{(1+e^{-x})'}{(1+e^{-x})^2}=\frac{1'+(e^{-x})'}{(1+e^{-x})^2}=\frac{0+(-x)'(e^{-x})}{(1+e^{-x})^2}=\frac{0+(-1)(e^{-x})}{(1+e^{-x})^2}=
=\frac{0-(e^{-x})}{(1+e^{-x})^2}=\frac{-e^{-x}}{(1+e^{-x})^2}
